{"type": "article", "id": 10654, "title": "Tiny Cloud 乌云音响吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-11T07:14:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606002011BtMhW5lrGesSv4b1.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这是一朵会唱歌还可以模拟雷电的……吊灯，是</span> <span></span><a href=\"http://www.richardclarkson.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Richard Clarkson </a><span><a href=\"http://www.richardclarkson.com/\" target=\"_blank\">设计工作室</a><span></span>为其之前 960 美元的 Smart cloud（</span><a href=\"http://www.richardclarkson.com/cloud\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以看视频</a><span>） 特别设计的迷你版本，</span><span>直径</span><span>约有 20 厘米。内置可以变色的LED彩灯、蓝牙控制音响和四种模式——灯光、音乐、阴影灯光模式、demo模式（所有效果一起开）。每朵Tiny Cloud都是手工制作拥有不同的形状，想象一下打开这朵乌云，营造一种下雨的氛围，雨声、雷电、乌云都有了，酷炫吗？（</span><a href=\"http://www.richardclarkson.com/shop/tiny-cloud\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a><span>）<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060020071rf48QyGCPwjxWD3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002007ZbGim56xNlE4cJLU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606060020081GMqpTameS3EhiWD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002008FRcWfVihTB0z46Yt.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002011K9FJjC1oOEtkD5Il.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}